Privacy Policy

Last updated: 28/12/2025
This Privacy Policy describes how the app (“the App”) handles your information.

1. Overview

The App is designed with privacy as a core principle.
All data processing is performed locally on your device.
We do not collect, store, transmit, or share your personal data on external servers.

2. Data Collection

The App does not collect any personal data.

Specifically:

We do not collect names, email addresses, phone numbers, or identifiers

We do not collect Slack account data on our servers

We do not track users

We do not use analytics, ads, or third-party trackers

3. Local Data Storage

Messages imported into the App are:

Stored only on your device

Indexed locally using a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) system

Used solely to allow you to interact with the AI and ask questions about your own data

This data never leaves your device.

4. AI Processing

AI interactions are handled in a privacy-preserving manner:

Message content is processed locally or sent only as necessary to provide AI responses

No message history is stored on our servers

We do not use your data to train AI models

5. Data Sharing

We do not sell, rent, share, or disclose your data to:

Third parties

Advertisers

Analytics providers

Affiliates

Your data belongs to you and remains private.

6. Data Deletion

You can delete all stored data at any time by:

Removing messages from within the App

Uninstalling the App, which permanently removes all locally stored data

7. Children’s Privacy

The App is not intended for use by children under the age of 13.
We do not knowingly collect data from children.

8. Security

We take reasonable measures to protect your data:

Local storage only

No external databases

No remote access to your information

However, no method of storage is 100% secure, and device security remains the user’s responsibility.

9. Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time.
Any changes will be reflected by updating the “Last updated” date.

10. Contact

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:

Email: lirazhad@gmail.com
